test/meson.build: link with audio_format.c

Fixes linker error since commit bfe9b361730fffad298484a29227e4e95821734d

contrib/mpc-completion.bash: override $MPC_FORMAT

If the user has set $MPC_FORMAT, this shouldn't break the bash
completion.

Closes https://github.com/MusicPlayerDaemon/mpc/issues/94

contrib/mpc-completion.bash: escape the string for use in the "sed" regular expression

Another fix for parentheses.
contrib/mpc-completion.bash: remove "eval" call, fixes filenames with paranetheses
contrib/mpc-completion.bash: pass "--" to mpc to allow parameters with dash
options: support long options without short option
use SPDX IDs, replacing the long copyright headers
.github/workflows/build.yml: remove the "Unit Tests" step because tests are disabled
